    <h1 class="opener__hed  -is-over-bg opener__hed--light opener__hed--small" >        Philips Kept Complaints About Dangerous Breathing Machines Secret While Company Profits Soared
    </h1>

    
            <div class="article-meta-1  -is-over-bg article-meta-1--light">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/debbie-cenziper">Debbie Cenziper</a>, ProPublica; <span class="name">Michael D. Sallah</span>, <span class="name">Michael Korsh</span> and <span class="name">Evan Robinson-Johnson</span>, <a href="http://www.post-gazette.com/">Pittsburgh Post-Gazette</a>;  and <span class="name">Monica Sager</span>, Northwestern University            </span>
            <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-09-27EDT06:00">Sept. 27, 6 a.m. EDT</time>
            </time>
        </div>
    
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

        <div class="content"> <!-- not sure if this is the best way to reestablish the text column -->
        <h2 class="opener__dek opener__dek--match-text-column" >            Tainted CPAP machines and ventilators went to children, the elderly and at least 700,000 veterans despite internal warnings. Company insiders said the devices posed an “unacceptable” risk.
        </h2>
    </div>
    
</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left      article-meta-1--hide-byline " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
        by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/debbie-cenziper">Debbie Cenziper</a>, ProPublica; <span class="name">Michael D. Sallah</span>, <span class="name">Michael Korsh</span> and <span class="name">Evan Robinson-Johnson</span>, <a href="http://www.post-gazette.com/">Pittsburgh Post-Gazette</a>;  and <span class="name">Monica Sager</span>, Northwestern University    </span>
    <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
