        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/breach-of-trust">Breach of Trust</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/concerned-about-obgyn-visit-heres-what-should-happen">
                                    Concerned About Your OB-GYN Visit? A Guide to What Should Happen — and What Shouldn’t.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            As we’ve reported on sexual misconduct by OB-GYNs, many women told us they didn’t know what was normal. With the help of providers, patients and experts, we created this guide.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/adriana-gallardo">Adriana Gallardo</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Jessica Miller</span>, <a href="https://www.sltrib.com/">The Salt Lake Tribune</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-09-15EDT08:00">Sept. 15, 8 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    


                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/north-carolina-gender-affirming-care-coverage-federal-appeal">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%273%27%20height%3D%272%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
