    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/the-hidden-fee-costing-doctors-millions-every-year">
                                    The Hidden Fee Costing Doctors Millions Every Year
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            A powerful lobbyist convinced a federal agency that doctors can be forced to pay fees on money that health insurers owe them. Big companies rake in profits while doctors are saddled with yet another cost in a burdensome health care system.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/cezary-podkul">Cezary Podkul</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-08-14EDT05:00">Aug. 14, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
